  <summary date="2018-04-06T18:26:24Z" status="Introduced in House">Planes Ensuring Total Safety Act or the PETS Act 

This bill directs the Federal Aviation Administration to promulgate regulations: (1) prohibiting the storage of a live animal in an overhead compartment of a flight in air transportation, and (2) establishing fines for a violation of such prohibition.</summary>
